		<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-388952">
		<div id="comment-388952">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/42d883528d90e50f9217ec3e5d99cc0a?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/42d883528d90e50f9217ec3e5d99cc0a?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.amazingstoriesmag.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>steve davidson</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
			<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="index.html#comment-388952">
				May 9, 2015 at 08:14					</a>
